uientry.unicode: Unit size||This displays the current unit size compared to the maximum unit size. Units will replenish over time when in owned territory, or when in certain stances.
Kills||The number of kills this unit has made in this battle. Kills will count toward a unit's XP.
Unit Experience||The higher a unit's rank, the more effective they will be in battle.
XP progress||This is the unit's progress towards gaining the next XP rank.
Upkeep||This amount will be deducted from your {{tr:icon_treasury}}{{tr:treasury}} each turn while this unit exists.
